It's just so...

32
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,313
random.

33
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:33,395
<i>(Abe laughs) Nice job.</i>

34
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,795
<i>I'm the king.</i>

