55
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,358
<i>Goodbye.</i>

56
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,993
<i>(machine beeps)</i>

57
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:19,989
<i>(man) Christ, Abe, don't do anything</i>
