243
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:54,276
<i>(static buzzes)</i>

244
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:25,112
Shit!

245
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:33,634
- Two weeks? That's so far.
- I know.

246
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:36,320
- I'll have to come.
- Yeah.

247
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:42,515
Ugh! OK. Three-martini lunches,
here I come.

248
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:47,032
