in my hotel room, you know what I mean?

252
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:06,559
- Hey, come on.
- Just leave it.

253
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:09,069
All right, that's enough.

254
00:32:10,080 --> 00:32:12,116
- Stop it!
- Get him!

255
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:16,279
