Stop it, you're hurting him!

256
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:24,837
Hey! Hey!

257
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,713
- Hey!
- <i>(man)</i> Shit! Guys, guys!

258
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:30,751
Hey!

259
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:38,276
- Help! Help!
- Let's go.

260
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:40,391
I'm slipping!

261
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:42,909
Please, pull me up.

262
00:32:43,040 --> 00:32:45,349
Pull me up!

263
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,756
Are you OK?

264
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,990
Yeah, he's gonna be fine.

265
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:08,230
Me, I'm not so sure about.

266
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:27,031
<i>(Marty) Abe, I missed you at work today.</i>
<i>I guess you decided to take that time off.</i>

267
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:30,311
<i>Give me a call when you get a chance,</i>
<i>all right? Later.</i>

268
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:33,352
Playing God for another day.

269
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:47,918
- <i>Hello?</i>
- Hey, Marty.

270
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:51,430
I'm on my way to the hospital
to check on that kid I helped earlier.

271
00:33:51,560 --> 00:33:54,120
- Would you meet me there?
- <i>Uh, yeah. Sure.</i>

272
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,390
Great. And...

273
00:33:57,840 --> 00:34:00,559
that stuff you're holding for me,

274
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,910
will you bring it?

275
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:04,917
I'm ready.

276
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:07,474
- <i>OK, sure.</i>
- Thanks.

277
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:11,197
<i>(elevator door pings)</i>

278
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:16,195
Hey.

279
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,469
<i>(Marty)</i> Hey.

280
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:22,071
- Thank you very much for meeting me.
- No problem, man.

281
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:25,112
There are things in here
that are gonna reopen wounds.

282
00:34:25,240 --> 00:34:27,549
- Are you sure you're ready?
- I'm positive.

283
00:34:27,680 --> 00:34:30,148
- OK.
- Thanks.

284
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:33,829
- Hey, call me if you need anything.
- I will.

285
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:41,231
Hey there.

286
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:45,069
- Oh, hey. Mr. Dale.
