287
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:47,430
Needed stitches, a few scrapes, bruises,

288
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:51,678
and we're doing a keep overnight
to make sure there's no concussion...

289
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:54,519
- <i>(voices echo)</i>
- ...but he should be fine.

290
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:56,870
<i>(echoing voices continue)</i>

291
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,911
Thanks.

292
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:16,550
<i>(echoing voices continue)</i>

293
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:47,752
<i>(voices get louder)</i>

294
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:52,471
<i>(voices whisper)</i>

295
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:06,437
Oh, come on.

296
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,191
