471
00:58:29,080 --> 00:58:31,196
2.50?

472
00:58:32,080 --> 00:58:33,115
You got ripped off.

473
00:58:37,160 --> 00:58:39,435
Eight ball, corner pocket.

474
00:58:45,360 --> 00:58:46,554
OK.

475
00:58:46,680 --> 00:58:49,035
How about double or nothing?

476
00:58:50,080 --> 00:58:52,036
All right.

477
00:58:54,400 --> 00:58:56,834
Rack 'em up, big boy.

478
00:59:17,600 --> 00:59:19,238
- Sorry.
