566
01:08:32,680 --> 01:08:34,398
<i>(feedback screeches)</i>

567
01:08:38,280 --> 01:08:40,794
<i>(echoing voices) If save, must kill.</i>

568
01:08:40,920 --> 01:08:43,878
<i>Must kill. Must kill. Must kill.</i>

569
01:08:52,320 --> 01:08:53,799
<i>(car horn)</i>

570
01:08:59,680 --> 01:09:03,229
<i>(aggressive, discordant music)</i>

571
01:09:14,200 --> 01:09:16,156
Kurt. Kurt.

572
01:09:16,280 --> 01:09:18,236
Kurt!

573
01:09:32,520 --> 01:09:34,636
I'm terribly sorry.

574
01:09:37,040 --> 01:09:38,758
I sincerely apologize.

575
01:09:50,440 --> 01:09:52,556
I'm sorry. I apologize.

576
01:09:57,960 --> 01:09:59,678
