01:10:08,200 --> 01:10:10,191
- <i>(man #4)</i> Let's go!
- <i>(woman screams)</i>

580
01:10:12,240 --> 01:10:16,438
- <i>(man #1)</i> Just put the gun down.
- <i>(man #2)</i> Other side. Other side.

581
01:10:17,640 --> 01:10:20,154
- Easy.
- Kurt!

582
01:10:26,480 --> 01:10:28,436
