583
01:10:28,560 --> 01:10:31,552
Go, go, go! Now!
I got him. I got him.

584
01:10:33,560 --> 01:10:38,588
- Keep calm. Slowly exit the building.
- This way, please.

585
01:10:44,760 --> 01:10:47,752
Hold on. Kurt!

586
01:10:47,880 --> 01:10:50,394
Kurt, what's wrong? Kurt!

587
01:10:52,320 --> 01:10:54,595
Kurt!

588
01:11:05,360 --> 01:11:06,679
